pFUnit
======

* NOTE(bja, 2014-01) The development version of pFUnit includes changes that break with gfortran < 4.8.3. To continue supporting gfortran 4.7, we have to use the branch pfunit_2.1.0

* updating:

cd ${PFLOTRAN_DIR}/tpls
git clone git://git.code.sf.net/p/pfunit/code pfunit
git checkout pfunit_2.1.0
git log --pretty="%H" -1 HEAD

git checkout fa37eebb
cd pfunit
make F90=gfortran-mp-4.8
./tests/tests.x
